{"tid":1578714,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"超重要超緊急, 向美國要求通過最辣香港人權及民主法案版本","createTime":"2019-09-18T08:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T16:52:41.000Z","uid":76310,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"98308d0b83c8d1416e594b01ae0f96ead220ca0c","tid":1578714,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:50:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/support-full-sanctions-parties-under-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsupport-full-sanctions-parties-under-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-2019&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evjze9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=17f1e3ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/support-full-sanctions-parties-under-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-2019</a><br />\n<br />\n大家快些簽名香港人權及民主法案, 要求最辣版本, 唔可以減辣<br />\n趁仲有時間, 一定要快, 向美國表達我地既意見<br />\n<br />\n另外順便簽埋要求中国還錢聯署, 爭二萬五咋<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evjze9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=c4c86ba8\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond</a>"},{"pid":"0b850575b44525bc5a30e62796c1a45eadc86833","tid":1578714,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8bdd0913c550b52d7f654e6679081eabece38a","tid":1578714,"uid":98141,"like":0,"dislike"