"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:29:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f7a71ef7f1bb9228575ec10583629d8b7c005b33","tid":1578714,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b5b418750cecd6a0f7d8718f5e60b661f15ed8","tid":1578714,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:38:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33d944185f1be9389780f9ad04a850f07f357e97","tid":1578714,"uid":155784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:52:41.000Z","msg":"美國最棘的制裁係唔俾你掂美金。即係所有跨國銀行(hsbc, Citi, scb) 唔俾開戶口。被制裁的人的錢都變成黑錢。<br />\n<br />\n因為咁其他銀行因為怕美國話佢地洗黑錢都未必俾你開戶。<br />\n<br />\n想像下林鄭，何妖，popo戶口都開唔到。國泰黨鐵被列入制裁，可以直接執笠。"}]}